  "detailed_description": "<h1>♥♥ ADD IN WISHLIST!! ♥♥</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>\"Masarada Town Story\" is an all-age RPG game developed by Sugar Star★ and published by BokiBoki Games!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168490/extras/f3bbb73c13c531234a0959cece2f88f3.avif?t=1774432437\" width=600 height=434 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story</h2>This is Masarada Town.<br>It is a lonely town that few tourists visit.<br><br>The birth rate in the town continued to decline, and young people were leaving town for the city.<br>The old people who have supported the town for a long time are getting older, and the population aging is getting worse.<br>If it goes on like this, will the town disappear like this?<br><br>The mayor decided to inject new blood into the town.<br>To unearth all the charm of this town, study the geography and find folklore<br>As a result of various investigations, there are many rare and rare stones here.<br>If a museum were built and these rare stones displayed, people would definitely gather in this town!<br><br>That's why I, Takarayama Jewel, were sent to this small town to work hard to mine rare ores!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168490/extras/949ea1ef4014e5806a6fd962caf58ae0.avif?t=1774432437\" width=180 height=180 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168490/extras/c1429051779f6ee9efab105b6143a7b2.avif?t=1774432437\" width=180 height=180 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168490/extras/b2c4aaad2d30e1d3d9f3be20eeec4be3.avif?t=1774432437\" width=180 height=180 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168490/extras/ee40abab18b89e884a5ba838515d4a92.avif?t=1774432437\" width=180 height=180 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168490/extras/d55f535065750c4208802ca54b3f4da5.avif?t=1774432437\" width=180 height=180 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168490/extras/d61882411d838b1db29bbe7b5af394fb.avif?t=1774432437\" width=180 height=180 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168490/extras/f51404a25756563b410245ed9f3650da.avif?t=1774432437\" width=600 height=316 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168490/extras/b5fe3e144169a455e38a76e606b4aa50.avif?t=1774432437\" width=600 height=472 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Relaxing small town RPG game<br></li><li>Explore the map<br></li><li>Collect assorted stones<br></li><li>Increase town prestige<br></li><li>Improve the goodwill of residents<br></li><li>Upgrade your gear<br></li><li>Fight various monsters</li></ul>   ",
  "about_the_game": "\"Masarada Town Story\" is an all-age RPG game developed by Sugar Star★ and published by BokiBoki Games!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168490/extras/f3bbb73c13c531234a0959cece2f88f3.avif?t=1774432437\" width=600 height=434 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story</h2>This is Masarada Town.<br>It is a lonely town that few tourists visit.<br><br>The birth rate in the town continued to decline, and young people were leaving town for the city.<br>The old people who have supported the town for a long time are getting older, and the population aging is getting worse.<br>If it goes on like this, will the town disappear like this?<br><br>The mayor decided to inject new blood into the town.<br>To unearth all the charm of this town, study the geography and find folklore<br>As a result of various investigations, there are many rare and rare stones here.<br>If a museum were built and these rare stones displayed, people would definitely gather in this town!<br><br>That's why I, Takarayama Jewel, were sent to this small town to work hard to mine rare ores!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168490/extras/949ea1ef4014e5806a6fd962caf58ae0.avif?t=1774432437\" width=180 height=180 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168490/extras/c1429051779f6ee9efab105b6143a7b2.avif?t=1774432437\" width=180 height=180 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168490/extras/b2c4aaad2d30e1d3d9f3be20eeec4be3.avif?t=1774432437\" width=180 height=180 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168490/extras/ee40abab18b89e